snippet: Devin Obee hit a three-run homer to help Bowling Green, Ky., beat Portland, Ore., 7-5, in an elimination game in the Little League World Series in South Williamsport, Pa.
abstract: Bowling Green, Ky, defeats Portland, Ore, 7-5, in elimination game in Little League World Series in South Williamsport, Pa.
